  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个事件驱动架构的时序图，核心流程是：Aggregate产生事件后写入Event Store，然后有个Reactor组件把事件转换成任务推到Queue里，最后Queue Worker消费并执行Side Effect。重点是失败要有重试机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下参与者顺序：Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect。确认一下，Reactor和Queue Worker是两个独立的角色吗？还是Worker直接监听Event Store？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是两个独立的。Reactor负责解耦，它从Event Store订阅事件，然后Push Job到Queue。Queue Worker是独立部署的进程，从Queue里Process Job。这样架构更灵活，Worker可以水平扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：Aggregate Store Event到Event Store，然后Dispatch Event给Reactor，Reactor Push Job到Queue，Queue Worker Process Job，最后Execute Side Effect。现在需要处理你说的重试机制，是用alt分支表示成功和失败两种情况吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用alt分支。成功路径：Side Effect返回Success后，Worker要Mark Job as Completed。失败路径：返回Failure，然后Worker触发Retry Job。注意重试是Queue层面的行为，不是无限循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。alt Success分支：S返回Success给W，然后W标记Q里的Job为Completed。else Failure分支：S返回Failure给W，W让Q重试Job。这样符合你的设计吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "有个细节要修正——Mark Job as Completed应该是Worker通知Queue去标记，不是Worker自己标记。所以箭头方向是W到Q，不是W自己闭环。另外Retry Job也是W通知Q重试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，已调整：W→Q Mark Job as Completed，以及W→Q Retry Job。现在整个流程完整了：从Aggregate产生事件，经过Event Store、Reactor、Queue，到Worker执行Side Effect，成功则标记完成，失败则触发重试。还有需要补充的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
